      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">52.232-37</ph> Multiple Payment Arrangements.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p " id="d3535e8">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="32.1110.dita#FAR_32_1110"
                     base="i1080821"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">32.1110</xref>(e)</ph>, insert the following clause:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" id="d3535e15">Multiple Payment Arrangements <ph outputclass="SmCaps" class="- topic/ph ">(May 1999)</ph>
         </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">This contract or agreement provides for payments to the Contractor through several alternative methods. The applicability of specific methods of payment and the designation of the payment office(s) are either stated-</p>
         <ol id="d3491e28" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3535e23">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            Elsewhere in this contract or agreement; or</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3535e28">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            In individual orders placed under this contract or agreement.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Endofclause">(End of clause)</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
